text: Egmating is a community in the Upper Bavarian district of Ebersberg in Germany. It is a member of the administrative community (Verwaltungsgemeinschaft) of Glonn. ==Geography== Egmating is in the Munich region. It includes one traditional rural land unit – Gemarkung in German – also called Egmating. ==References== Category:Ebersberg (district)
title: Egmating
